snippet.description:
PLANET DOLAN characters come together to COMPETE for the single greatest kart run EVER! Download FREE today and join the race!
Android ► https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chunkworks.dolankart&hl=en
Apple ► https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dolan-kart/id1316860571

FEATURES:
- Play as the Planet Dolan cast and collect SHINIES to unlock characters & skins
- Ride in a kart, or on a giant turtle, or even on an Australian cassowary
- Simple, addictive pick-up-and-go gameplay
- Use a variety of powerups such as Dark Magic, turning obstacles into REWARDS!
- Bash into bees and then BECOME A BEE!
- Compete against players & friends scores on an international leaderboard
- Explore levels: Gooby Greens and Snewpee Shore

Please remember to report bugs and issues by emailing support@chunk.works - we're happy to help!

Would like to thank:
@Cernji from Chunk Works for his incredible hard work bringing this project to life (he's a one man developer army), AND
@CamMRooney for setting all of this up (+ for designing the WICKED DK logo!).
@NG_Tyler for his amazing sprite & level work
@HelloImElaine and @jamesharknado for the UI design and intro animation
@honeeybits for her key character/skin art
@chayadol2006 for the INSANE poster art & various kart designs, wow!
And a super special shoutout to our Dolan Kart audio guys, @JONFORESTMUSIC from @SoundPitchAU and, of course, the original Dolan Kart theme composer @Durawks - sorry if I missed anyone!

